{"tid":1583193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"你地肯醒未？","createTime":"2019-09-20T13:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T13:41:50.000Z","uid":278392,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1567c26010aa429ab7be8b60427ce95265412d","tid":1583193,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:08:10.000Z","msg":"聽日已經係星期六<br />\n行動po呢？<br />\n熱門發生咩事？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZxXYcm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZxXYcm.png&h=c8d9fb99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1975fbf048e8a76f13cb0ad463c6d9c730208f67","tid":1583193,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1xckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=bd32710b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1xckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=88e63c6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"ecdab3f29d9dc9a38cccc5d530235b32641abfaf","tid":1583193,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:08:40.000Z","msg":"政府借減碳排放為名，話要向中國買電<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"5ede063d538d8dbe3bd15070f69a83dc951fa3a7","tid":1583193,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8026ef5f28cb9def0811f65e05b12ce389612821","tid":1583193,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bfc8f12e77d00dc07d9bab6581357b3a87cdfa2","tid":1583193,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a1664cfc464581e750872d982a80f1e0c23195","tid":1583193,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc086ff5b57e01e1e4c0a1138e96c1806282f276","tid":1583193,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: